actor_user:
Task: {{ goal }}
Context: {{ context }}
Slice: {{ slice_id }}
Produce: (1) A short analysis, (2) a unified diff patch that implements the change, (3) brief instructions for reviewers. Return JSON with keys: analysis, patch, instructions, confidence.

observer_user:
Task: {{ goal }}
Context: {{ context }}
Slice: {{ slice_id }}
ActorOutput: {{ actor_output | default('') }}
Evaluate the Actor output for correctness, security, and risk. Return JSON with keys: verdict (OK/CAUTION/REJECT), findings (list), risk_level (low/medium/high), recommended_changes (string).
